      "content": "but taking a step back feels like it’s not enough. like, \"taking a break\" implies there's something left to come back to. but there isn't. the money's gone, my reputation is trashed, and my family just thinks i'm \"struggling\" but they don't get that there's nothing to struggle for anymore. it's just a void. i'm just so exhausted with the constant effort of existing when everything i've built is just... dust.",
